# 9point75 Woodworks LLC - Website Build Roadmap
**Platform:** Next.js on GitHub -> Vercel
**Domain:** Cloudflare -> Vercel
**Launch Target:** April 30, 2026

## Phase 1
- Establish design system and reusable layout
- Build mobile-first public pages
- Add placeholder content where assets are not ready

## Phase 2
- Complete homepage and gallery experience
- Draft initial copy
- Build contact form shape and admin shell

## Phase 3
- Connect Supabase auth, storage, and submissions
- Add owner dashboard for lead review and gallery management
- Replace placeholders with final project photography

## Phase 4
- Performance, accessibility, SEO, and launch prep
